  "body": "End-of-session closeout for 2026-05-23. Shipped: (1) standalone cc-ninja-capture CLI (fourth capture transport, covers Claude Code from CLI / desktop GUI / any Claude-Code-aware editor, includes --include-subagents for nested traces), (2) parser+formatter promoted from vscode/ to core/, (3) VS Code extension v0.16.0–v0.16.4 with multi-Claude-tab routing (auto-detect role-id from active tab label via viewType==='mainThreadWebview-claudeVSCodePanel'), and (4) versioning-discipline rule established as a MUST. Five load-bearing learnings recorded: (1) filesystem-read works for Claude Code but not for Claude Desktop (the Electron app stores no conversation history locally — only the user's draft), (2) tab-label-as-role-id is solvable but tab-to-JSONL matching isn't (Anthropic.claude-code v2.1.145 publishes exports:undefined; Director chose option D / accept the gap), (3) name actions after the dominant signal (Director caught my 'Save Focused Chat' misnaming — content comes from JSONL recency, not focus; renamed to 'Save Most Recent Chat'), (4) gitignore build-copy destinations from day one (almost committed cli/src/core/ and server/src/core/ before catching it), (5) diagnostics MUST surface the version. Outstanding items minor / cosmetic. Full design rationale, rejected alternatives, and follow-ups in the sibling .body.md. Pushed as commit bfa4bac.",

